readable.content: a brown dog is jumping up at a woman in a black coat . A dog jumps for the woman 's treat . A large black and white dog jumps up to get something held by a woman wearing a black jacket . a woman teaches a dog to jump for treats , outside on the grass . A woman with a vest and red shirt is holding her hand up above a black and white dog that is jumping .
